claim.claim-text:
3. A mask manufactured by the method of claim 1, the mask comprising:
a mask body having an upper end provided with a nose contact part; and
ear loop strings that are respectively provided at both sides of the mask body,
wherein the mask body comprises:
an inner surface sheet having various colors;
an outer surface sheet having a color different from a color of the inner surface sheet;
a diamond-shaped portion provided on the inner surface sheet along a horizontal length direction of the mask body;
first extension portions respectively provided at an upper portion and a lower portion of the diamond-shaped portion;
a linear-shaped portion provided on the outer surface sheet along the horizontal length direction of the mask body; and
second extension portions respectively provided at an upper portion and a lower portion of the linear-shaped portion.
